{"analytics_identifier":null,"base_path":"/government/organisations/office-for-the-internal-market/about/our-governance","content_id":"c8f52773-c48a-4531-827a-33b6423919c0","description":"","details":{"attachments":[],"body":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>The <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/office-for-the-internal-market\" class=\"govuk-link\">Office for the Internal Market</a> (OIM) is part of the Competition and Markets Authority (CMA). The OIM Panel assists the OIM in carrying out its functions, as set out in the UK Internal Market Act. The Chair of the OIM Panel, <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/people/murdoch-maclennan\" class=\"govuk-link\">Murdoch MacLennan</a>, sits on the CMA Board.</p>\n\n<h3 id=\"oim-panel-members\">OIM Panel members</h3>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>\n    <p><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/oim-panel-member-biographies-and-disclosures-of-interest/panel-members-biographies#professor-andreas-stephan\" class=\"govuk-link\">Professor Andreas Stephan</a></p>\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <p><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/oim-panel-member-biographies-and-disclosures-of-interest/panel-members-biographies#angharad-butler\" class=\"govuk-link\">Angharad Butler</a></p>\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <p><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/oim-panel-member-biographies-and-disclosures-of-interest/panel-members-biographies#michael-neilson\" class=\"govuk-link\">Michael Neilson</a></p>\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <p><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/oim-panel-member-biographies-and-disclosures-of-interest/panel-members-biographies#shane-lynch\" class=\"govuk-link\">Shane Lynch</a></p>\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <p><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/oim-panel-member-biographies-and-disclosures-of-interest/panel-members-biographies#stephen-gifford\" class=\"govuk-link\">Stephen Gifford</a></p>\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <p><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/oim-panel-member-biographies-and-disclosures-of-interest/panel-members-biographies#professor-suzanne-rab\" class=\"govuk-link\">Professor Suzanne Rab</a></p>\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <p><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/oim-panel-member-biographies-and-disclosures-of-interest/panel-members-biographies#tim-render\" class=\"govuk-link\">Tim Render</a></p>\n  </li>\n</ul>\n</div>","change_history":[{"note":"First published.","public_timestamp":"2021-09-21T10:02:31Z"}],"organisation":"b1123ceb-77e4-40fc-9526-83ad0ba7cf01","tags":{"browse_pages":[]}},"document_type":"our_governance","first_published_at":"2021-09-21T11:02:31+01:00","links":{"available_translations":[{"api_path":"/api/content/government/organisations/office-for-the-internal-market/about/our-governance","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/government/organisations/office-for-the-internal-market/about/our-governance","base_path":"/government/organisations/office-for-the-internal-market/about/our-governance","content_id":"c8f52773-c48a-4531-827a-33b6423919c0","document_type":"our_governance","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2021-09-21T10:02:31Z","schema_name":"corporate_information_page","title":"Our governance","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/office-for-the-internal-market/about/our-governance","withdrawn":false}],"organisations":[{"analytics_identifier":"OT1340","api_path":"/api/content/government/organisations/office-for-the-internal-market","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/government/organisations/office-for-the-internal-market","base_path":"/government/organisations/office-for-the-internal-market","content_id":"b1123ceb-77e4-40fc-9526-83ad0ba7cf01","details":{"acronym":"OIM","brand":"department-for-business-trade","default_news_image":null,"logo":{"crest":"custom","formatted_title":"Office for the Internal Market","image":{"alt_text":"Office for the Internal Market","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/61375a748fa8f503c6403da1/